list.abstract: probably（英 [ˈprɒbəbli]，美 [ˈprɑːbəbli]），英语单词，副词，意思为几乎可以肯定；很可能；大概。短语搭配有probably will（可能会）。例句为“We are probably immature and over-trusting.（我们可能不成熟，轻信于他人。）” probably相关近义词有possibly、maybe等，相关反义词有incredibly。

yingyinNormal.en: He probably just goes to the bathroom.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他可能只是去拉大号吧。

yingyinNormal.en: Probably. Wouldn't be the first time.
yingyinNormal.zh: 可能吧，又不是第一次了。

yingyinNormal.en: It is possible I will continue making hilarious mistakes. Probably.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我很可能会继续犯逗比错误。可能哦。

yingyinNormal.en: Probably serving food that was ordered today.
yingyinNormal.zh: 可能要上今天点的菜。

yingyinNormal.en: And you're right. In the end I'd probably lose.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你们说得对，最后我可能会输。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, she probably just wanted to see your mom's art.
yingyinNormal.zh: 她可能只是想看看你妈的画。

yingyinNormal.en: So you're probably wondering what that was all about.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你可能在琢磨刚才是怎么回事。

yingyinNormal.en: No,I haven't. Get used to it. Yeah. I probably won't.
yingyinNormal.zh: 没有，你会习惯的。我可能不会。

yingyinNormal.en: You all right? It's nothing. Probably just the altitude.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你还好吗？没事，可能是高原反应。

yingyinNormal.en: That smarts. Again? Yeah. Uh, it's probably just motion sickness.
yingyinNormal.zh: 真疼。又来吗？是啊，可能只是晕动病。

yingyinNormal.en: When do you think we lost her? Probably around gonorrhea.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你觉得她是什么时候离开的？可能是性病那一段吧。

yingyinNormal.en: Probably. Uh-huh. You see?
yingyinNormal.zh: 可能，你看到了吧？

yingyinNormal.en: So it's probably genetic.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那这可能是遗传的咯。

yingyinNormal.en: Probably not, I could see if I can get their new number there, but probably not.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不太可能，我可试试能否找到他们新号码，但希望不大。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, the next stage would probably be control of other people.
yingyinNormal.zh: 下一阶段可能是控制他人。

yingyinNormal.en: And snoring, and that's probably just a sinus infection. But it could be sleep apnea.
yingyinNormal.zh: 还有打呼，可能是有点鼻窦感染，但也有可能是睡眠呼吸暂停综合症。

yingyinNormal.en: Probably better if we don't talk about it. Right, of course.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我不告诉你可能比较好。行，那当然。

yingyinNormal.en: Does the aquarium have every type of fish? Oh, yes. Probably.
yingyinNormal.zh: 海洋馆有不同类型的鱼吗？是的。可能。

yingyinNormal.en: That's probably just some 12-year-old kid trying to get girls to call.
yingyinNormal.zh: 可能是想跟女生讲电话的12岁小鬼。

yingyinNormal.en: Probably, yeah. I mean, maybe we should hold off until we talk to Ross.
yingyinNormal.zh: 可能吧，我是说我们应该先和罗斯说清楚。
